# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:14
translate chinese izzy1_86459c4f:

    # "Okay, I'm going to do it. I'm going to go talk to them."
    "好吧，我决定做了。我要去跟他们说话。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:15
translate chinese izzy1_f33a08f7:

    # "I swallow my fear and walk casually up towards the people standing around the picnic tables."
    "我压下恐惧，若无其事地走向围在野餐桌旁的那群人。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:18
translate chinese izzy1_e6ebfaea:

    # "As soon as I begin to approach, they stop what they're doing and turn towards me."
    "我刚一靠近，他们就停下动作，转过身来。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:19
translate chinese izzy1_7899e502:

    # "They look intimidating, but I don't stop. I keep walking until I'm standing just a few yards away from them."
    "他们看起来很凶，但我没有停下。 我一直走，直到离他们只有几码远。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:23
translate chinese izzy1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_1_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_1_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:24
translate chinese izzy1_d20e163b:

    # gl "Where you going, twig-boy?"
    gl "“你要去哪儿，小树枝？”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:25
translate chinese izzy1_7d2401c7:

    # pc "Twig-boy?"
    pc "“小树枝？”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:27
translate chinese izzy1_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_1_2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_1_2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:28
translate chinese izzy1_d093d218:

    # gl "Yeah, cause you about the size of a twig and my guys could snap you in two."
    gl "“是啊，因为你跟树枝一样细，我这帮兄弟一掰就能把你掰成两截。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:29
translate chinese izzy1_aec5c4f7:

    # "I look over at them behind her. I almost believe that they could."
    "我瞥了眼她身后的那帮人。我几乎相信他们真能做到。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:30
translate chinese izzy1_51076f5a:

    # pc "I just thought I'd come over and say hi. I'm new in town."
    pc "“我只是想过来打个招呼。我是刚搬来这儿的。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:32
translate chinese izzy1_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_1_3.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_1_3.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:33
translate chinese izzy1_f9a04499:

    # gl "And you think we're the welcoming committee? We look like the type that'd invite you over, make you a casserole?"
    gl "你以为我们是欢迎委员会？我们看起来像是会邀请你来家里，给你做焗菜的那种人吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:35
translate chinese izzy1_23081509:

    # moose "Haha! A casserole! You so funny, Izzy."
    moose "哈哈！焗菜！伊兹，你真搞笑。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:37
translate chinese izzy1_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_1_4.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_1_4.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:38
translate chinese izzy1_c2c19747:

    # gl "Shut the fuck up, Moose."
    gl "闭上你的臭嘴，穆斯。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:39
translate chinese izzy1_33e887bb:

    # moose "Sorry, girl. My bad."
    moose "抱歉，姑娘。是我不对。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:42
translate chinese izzy1_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_1_5.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_1_5.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:43
translate chinese izzy1_f6a69cf1:

    # gl "Anyways, we ain't no city council and we ain't an open forum."
    gl "总之，我们既不是市议会，也不是公开论坛。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:45
translate chinese izzy1_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_1_6.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_1_6.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:46
translate chinese izzy1_671e7cca:

    # gl "So you ain't welcome here. Get it, Twig?"
    gl "所以你在这里不受欢迎。听明白了吗，特威格？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:51
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_bc94c85f:

    # gl "You back, Twig?"
    gl "你回来了，小树枝？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:52
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_5e16b4dd:

    # gl "I told you that you ain't welcome here."
    gl "我跟你说过，你在这儿不受欢迎。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:56
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_19da926c:

    # gl "Good. Get the fuck out of here, Twig."
    gl "好。赶紧滚蛋，小树枝。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:59
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_03a3489c:

    # "I turn and walk away. After I take a few steps I can hear them all laughing. It's humiliating."
    "我转身走开。走了几步，还能听到他们都在笑。真丢人。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:60
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_6aa25614:

    # "Maybe I'll try again some other time, but for now I just want to get out of here."
    "也许改天我再试一次，但现在我只想赶紧离开这里。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:70
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_ea29e717:

    # gl "Oh, is that what you think?"
    gl "哦，你是这么想的？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:71
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_4f1631c8:

    # gl "Fine. Moose, grab him."
    gl "行。穆斯，抓住他。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:72
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_c7045d3c:

    # moose "You got it, girl."
    moose "没问题，姑娘。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:75
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_bfacd7f0:

    # "With unnatural speed for his size, the big man charges towards me, arms out."
    "那个大块头以与他体型不相称的速度朝我冲来，双臂张开。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:77
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_d623de1c:

    # "Without even thinking about it, I turn and run the other way."
    "我没多想，转身朝相反方向跑去。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:78
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_c857d906:

    # "He gives chase for a bit, but then gives up and goes back to the others."
    "他追了一会儿，但随后放弃了，回到了其他人身边。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:81
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_2a2c5fa4:

    # "I don't stop though. I just showed how much of a pussy I am by running there and now I can't just go back and face them again."
    "但我没有停下。刚才跑过去已经暴露了我有多懦弱，现在我不能就这么回去面对他们。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:82
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_224c9c2b:

    # gl "That's right, keep running, Twig!"
    gl "没错，继续跑啊，小树枝！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:83
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_67906573:

    # "She yells after me, taunting me as I head back towards my car."
    "她在我身后大喊，嘲讽着我走向自己的车。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:84
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_45a42840:

    # "Maybe if I was more confident, I could stand my ground, but for now I just want to get out of here."
    "也许如果我更有自信，就能挺住，但眼下我只想赶紧离开这里。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:85
translate chinese izzytwigtalk_9a4f14d6:

    # "I could probably boost my confidence by chatting up random strangers at the school café. That seems like the most obvious way."
    "我大概可以通过在学校咖啡厅和陌生人搭话来提升自信。这似乎是最显而易见的方法。"

